wiki.summary: “Calling My Spirit” is a song by Florida artist Kodak Black from his 2018 album Dying to Live. This song was produced by Southside and Jake-One. On this emotional track, Kodak talks about he has put his spirit in every song by him. He also talks about how the whole rap industry needs to sell their soul for actual attention and fame. Read more on Last.fm.
